<title>ḥbytny wạ̉nạ kẖạṭy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥbytny wạ̉nạ kẖạṭy hw ạ̉nạ myn wbrgẖm kẖyạnty knt ạlạ̉myn
 mʿ ạ̹ny jrḥtk wbʿdt ktyr lknk fy bʿdy knt ạlmʿyn
 ạlqrạr - wlạ gẖṣb ʿny wlạ qṣd mny byh ạ̉brr ạlwqwʿ
 mạ ạ̹nt sẖạmlny wlạ ywm ḥạrmny wbtmsḥ ʿn ʿyny ạldmwʿ
 dạymạaⁿ sẖạgẖlny wmḥyrny ḥbk ly wạ̉nạ fy wqt ạlrjwʿ
 2- wfy kl mrẗ brjʿ btqblny wlạ ywm btrfḍny wtʿạyrny
 wdạymạaⁿ tsạmḥ wtnsy̱ ly wlmạ bạsyb ạ̹ydk btmskny</lyrics>
</song>